title: Cuibém
body: This family name comes from Antonia Jaime Cuibém, who came to Madeira in 1590 with her husband, the Englishman Roberto Vizovi, a knight of the Order of Christ. This Vizovi established a business in Funchal.

Funchal: Location where Roberto Vizovi established a business

Antonia Jaime Cuibém: Person who came to Madeira in 1590

1590: Arrival of Antonia Jaime Cuibém in Madeira
